### Curl the scripts
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BennyOe/arch_install/main/install.sh
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BennyOe/arch_install/main/gui.sh

### Install Arch Linux
- install.sh installs the base arch system. The only thing you have to do manually ist in fdisk type the commands 
"g" 
3x "n" with the sizes "+500M" "+<RAMSIZE>M" "<REST>"
"t" with partition 1 set to "1" 
"t" with partition 2 set to "19"
"w" to write and quit.

### Install XOrg and DWM
with gui.sh
